data.description: This lovely Clarksburg as-is home with acreage has been renovated top to bottom in 2008.  Sip lemonade while you relax on your 3/4 wrap around porch. Highlights include: oversized first floor bathroom with radiant heat, jet tub, and custom walk in shower. Second floor laundry, and huge family room over the garage which boasts a stunning cultured stone bar and gas fireplace. A great spot to entertain! Buyer to pay for survey.
